## Unsafe Code Requirements

Every `unsafe` block requires a `// SAFETY:` comment explaining why the
invariants are upheld:

```rust
// SAFETY: The pointer is valid and aligned because [reason].
//         The lifetime is correct because [reason].
unsafe { ... }
```

Run `cargo geiger` to track the unsafe surface area. Do not increase it
without justification and peer review.
{{/if}}

