## Transport Security

All outbound connections use TLS 1.2 or higher. Use `rustls` rather than
OpenSSL defaults. Never disable certificate verification.

```rust
// WRONG — disables all certificate validation
// config.dangerous().with_custom_certificate_verifier(Arc::new(NoVerifier));

// CORRECT — use proper certificate verification
let tls_config = ClientConfig::builder()
    .with_root_certificates(root_store)
    .with_no_client_auth();
```

For test environments with self-signed certificates, add the test CA to the
trust store rather than disabling verification.
{{/if}}

