## Code Review Security Checklist

Before merging any change:

- [ ] No hardcoded secrets, API keys, or credentials
- [ ] All external input validated at the boundary
- [ ] Sensitive types use `secrecy::Secret` and `ZeroizeOnDrop`
- [ ] `unsafe` blocks have `// SAFETY:` comments
- [ ] Constant-time comparison used for secret values
- [ ] No new dependency added without security review
- [ ] `cargo audit` passes with no unresolved advisories
